               <p>JOHN LOVERIDGE. I live in <placeName id="t18230409-222-crimeloc1186">Crawford-street, Mary-le-bone</placeName>
                  <interp inst="t18230409-222-crimeloc1186" type="placeName" value="Crawford-street, Mary-le-bone"></interp>
                  <interp inst="t18230409-222-crimeloc1186" type="type" value="crimeLocation"></interp>
                  <join result="offencePlace" targOrder="Y" targets="t18230409-222-off1184 t18230409-222-crimeloc1186"></join>. On the 27th of March, I was serving behind the counter, and saw the prisoner and another man come up and take a side of bacon from the door. I ran out and called Stop thief! The prisoner threw it down - I took it up, and two watchmen and I secured him. I am positive he is the person.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18230409-222-person1964">
